Khale is a CMS based on Ale based on Yaws.

Layout:
* Currently there's no GUI to change the layout, e.g. the positions of blocks.
  You have to edit the source code of the layout module manually.

== Install and Start

Install Erlang.

Install Ale (http://github.com/ngocdaothanh/ale) and Yaws
(http://wiki.github.com/klacke/yaws) to Erlang's lib directory

Run "make" to build.

== Run

Run "make migrate" to prepare DB schema.

Run "make start" to start.
